			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/08/05/as-long-as.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>“As long as these problems persist — a right marred by bigotry, a liberalism maddened by utopianism — it is hard to imagine a reasonable [immigration] deal.” —<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/08/05/opinion/sunday/trump-immigration-compromise-douthat.html?smprod=nytcore-ipad&amp;smid=nytcore-ipad-share\">Ross Douthat</a></p>\n",
